snippet.textDisplay:
GOD IS REALL!!! I have to write this down somewhere because Jesus is willing me to share how He changed my life here. I believe anyone who will read this, it is Jesus who brought you!
I was an atheist, never believed in God. I was clubbing, drinking, partying, doing all sorts of things in this world that made me happy and never found peace. The only result of me being the king of my life was death.
God is now calling everyone to repent and come back to Him! The time is coming when Jesus is coming soon.
Three years ago, in the moment of my spiritual death, I encountered Jesus and experienced His love and His presence. I realized that the devil deceived me until now so I won't be saved but stay as his slave!


I was a slave of sin and I knew I would go to hell. But God taught me the good news that Jesus Christ died on the cross and paid the price of my sin and now I am free! God changed me completely!!
He is real guys! The churches lost their power and love for God because of prosperity and compromising but all the things in the Bible will be fulfilled! The judgments are coming but God is delaying because He is calling some of you!


Listen, Jesus really really really died for you! He shed His own blood to cleanse you and give you a new life! We had to die because of our sins but God gave HIs only son so whoever believes Him will have eternal life and have restored relationship with God. He will transform you as you come to Jesus and ask Him to come into your life. Repent and surrender!

It's time to wake up!! Please please watch the prophecy done in 1973 by pastor David Wilkerson. So many things became true! There will so many tribulations and false teaching and satanic evangelists, economic recession, occults, and moral landslide BUT JESUS IS COMING! Those who fully surrender their life to Christ will experience healing from their hurts and become a child of God unstoppable!!


https://youtu.be/l_R9I-qQEbs
